  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study compared 10 weeks of treatment with olanzapine versus placebo in adolescent
      females with anorexia nervosa-restricting type who were undergoing acute treatment on an
      inpatient unit or a day hospital program that specializes in the treatment of eating
      disorders.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
